{"tid":1540394,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺林病個樣好似唔同左","createTime":"2019-09-04T11:24:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T11:52:11.000Z","uid":44893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ae89a363a46cd7c7446254cb26a601a5c1c2b663","tid":1540394,"uid":44893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:24:43.000Z","msg":"今日講撒回，下晝就無lala 上廣西 是咪已經死撚左所以搵個老臨講撇回想 了事。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nbtw 義士唔係condom<br />\n光復香港，時代革命。<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95b44cd7aa76c8df2ae665224ab86368363f5d78","tid":1540394,"uid":190406,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:30:06.000Z","msg":"有咩唔同<br />\n佢都係咁柒林<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee6c2b2459ab3da3630c09b7820a82f53e9e220a","tid":1540394,"uid":72800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:51:59.000Z","msg":"意氣風發<br />\n逐步出招 瓦解革命"},{"pid":"f858b053c274d33c28f92a78efb0f4d69c165ae9","tid":1540394,"uid":72800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:52:11.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">港共殺人政權企圖以<strong>錄音、撤回、學季開始</strong><br />\n轉移<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">太子地鐵傷亡、<br />\n六警壓脊椎休克 <span style=\"color: teal;\">至今嚴重昏迷</span>、<br />\n新屋嶺、<span style=\"color: violet;\">民主人權法案</span>、<br />\n臥底實彈、武警滲透、<span style=\"color: green;\">清朝債主權問題</span><br />\n</span></strong></span>連串<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>核彈</strong></span><span style=\"color: red;\">事件焦點<br />\n醒呀大家 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">政府帶緊風向</span><br />\n背後繼續大清算 入獄 利刑 一年後被失蹤</span></div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">林鄭錄音：事件現時已經上升至「國家主權及國家安全的層次，\n加上世界兩大經濟體前所未有的張力」，她可以做的已經非常少。</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\"><blockquote><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">英、美領事館請願 大遊行</span></span></strong><br />\n審視中英聯合聲明 法定性<br />\n中共正統性<br />\n中共毀約 無視國際社會<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">請求國際介入香港前途</span></span></strong> <br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">施壓制裁港府 還港人雙普選 <br />\n協助制定民主進程</span></span></strong><br />\n香港人道災難 高壓滅聲 白色恐怖 <br />\n執法機器無法無天 受命中共 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">港府管治班子失去自治權 聽命中央</span><br />\n實彈恐怖 威嚇扼殺<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">民主自由</span>現代普世價值<br />\n<strong>人權民主法案 事在必行</strong></blockquote></div><br />\n<br />\n#FiveDemands <br />\n#1down4togo<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">暗黑兵法劇本 出沒注意：\n\n沒收gear 未來兩星期大量武警喬裝示威者 嫁禍衝擊\n內部分化示威者、\n酷刑凌虐威嚇被捕人士、\n邊緣打壓香港 渲染港獨 阻抗爭之風蔓延內陸、\n假新聞、擺拍、編輯、洗腦文宣製造風向 污名化運動、\n暴力鎮壓 拘捕 扣留 私刑 企圖瓦解前線、\n文宣 抹黑 嫁禍 插贜 示威者、\n暗殺 第一滴血 企圖逆轉民意 國際譴責、\n市民絕望噤聲 憤怒冷卻、\n中立派 賺錢派 政治疲勞、\n鼓吹經濟下滑風向 富豪商家屈服 加速瓦解、\n學季始開，拖延 分散 擊破、\n白色恐怖、清除異己、染紅香港\n\n拖字訣 雨傘結局 ⋯</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>這不只是反修例活動<br />\n這是屬於香港人的<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">時代革命</span></strong></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">流水革命</span></strong></div>"}]}